data.description: THE SEARCH IS OVER! This Grand Southern Beauty located in sought out Cherokee Woods Cove is spacious and move in ready. It features a new kitchen with updated cabinets, stainless steel appliances, coffee/wine station and quartz counter tops. The main level also offers a large living room, separate dining and family room with a gas starter fireplace. Begin your morning by enjoying a nice cup of coffee or tea out on your screened in porch overlooking your private yard and views of Stone Mountain. As you venture upstairs, you will find a spacious Owners suite with an updated bathroom featuring his/her vanities, separate shower and spacious tub for soaking. All secondary bedrooms are generously sized and there is a bonus room that could be a home office, media room, craft room, etc. The bonus room can be easily accessed from the second staircase that comes up from the kitchen. Quiet neighborhood with swim/tennis and is close to tons of shopping! What's not to love?
